OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FITV News' Andy Bonner spent a day on
OL,7,Fthe Bee Network to see what those
OL,8,Fliving under the Andy Burnham
OL,9,FMayoralty think of him taking on the
OL,10,Ftop job.
OL,12,FVoters from across the North West say
OL,13,F"time will tell" whether Andy Burnham
OL,14,Fcan make the step up from Mayor of
OL,15,FGreater Manchester to the top job in
OL,16,FBritish politics.
OL,18,FOne month on from his win in the
OL,19,FMakerfield by-election, Andy Burnham
OL,20,Fis now leader of the Labour Party and
OL,21,Fprime minister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
