OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FOne of Mr Burnham's key priorities is
OL,7,Fdevolving power away from Westminster,
OL,8,Fwith a new "No 10 North" based in
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,11,FHe was dubbed 'King of the North'
OL,12,Fduring the Covid pandemic when he
OL,13,Fpublicly took on then Prime Minister
OL,14,FBoris Johnson over the decision to put
OL,15,FGreater Manchester into the highest
OL,16,Flevel of lockdown restrictions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
