OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FBurnham's integration of the transport
OL,7,Fsystem to form 'The Bee Network' made
OL,8,FGreater Manchester the first place
OL,9,Foutside of London to bring bus
OL,10,Fservices and other modes of transport
OL,11,Ftogether and back under public control.
OL,13,FBut does the ability to make the buses
OL,14,Frun on time give Andy Burnham the
OL,15,Fskills he needs to run the country?
OL,17,FOn Burnham's Bee Network:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, those taking the
OL,7,Fbus in Greater Manchester seemed
OL,8,Flargely hopeful about Andy Burnham
OL,9,Frunning the country.
OL,11,FOne voter who lives in Leigh - where
OL,12,FBurnham served as MP from 2010 - 2017
OL,13,F- said: "I would hope he's got the
OL,14,Fqualities to lead the country.
OL,16,F"Becoming Prime Minister is a very
OL,17,Fdifferent kind of sauce to what you
OL,18,Fsee most people doing. Just like with
OL,19,FKeir Starmer, people hoped he had that
OL,20,Fkind of quality which I don't
OL,21,Fnecessarily think he did.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,F"I guess it's going to be something
OL,7,Fthat time will tell really."
OL,9,FAnother man said he thinks Mr Burnham
OL,10,Fwill be a better leader than his
OL,11,Fpredecessor Keir Starmer.
OL,13,FHe said: "I think he seems quite
OL,14,Fgenuine and seems to want to do more
OL,15,Fthan the other fella. He's done quite
OL,16,Fgood things in Manchester with the bus
OL,17,Ffares and what have you."
OL,19,FOne woman agreed that she had more
OL,20,Fhope in Burnham than in Keir Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FShe said: "I think he's great, you
OL,7,Fonly have to see what he's done in
OL,8,FManchester. I think he's down to
OL,9,Fearth, he's one of us.
OL,11,F"Keir Starmer was all for down South,
OL,12,Fhe didn't care about us up here,
OL,13,Fnothing got done and we didn't get
OL,14,Fanything so we're hoping Andy will
OL,15,Flook on us favourably."
OL,17,FOutside of Burnham's Greater
OL,18,FManchester bubble:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
