PN,36907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FIn Burnley, views were mixed on
OL,7,Fwhether Andy Burnham's success as
OL,8,FMayor of Greater Manchester could
OL,9,Ftransfer to succeeding as Prime
OL,10,FMinister.
OL,12,FLike much of the North West, Burnley
OL,13,Fis a traditional safe seat for Labour
OL,14,Fthat has seen growing support for
OL,15,FReform UK.
OL,17,FThis makes it a key area where Andy
OL,18,FBurnham has promised to win back
OL,19,Fvoters in the next General Election,
OL,20,Fbut so far many are still sceptical.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FOne man said: "The world's in a mess,
OL,7,Fthey're not going to change anything.
OL,8,FI think he'll be good for everybody
OL,9,Fbut it's the world that's the problem,
OL,10,Fnot Labour."
OL,12,FAnother agreed, telling ITV News: "I
OL,13,Fthink Labour will try to do well in
OL,14,FBurnley but there are a lot of
OL,15,Fproblems and it takes time to solve
OL,16,Fthem so good luck to him."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FOne man said: "I think once they go
OL,7,Fdown there they get wrapped up down
OL,8,Fthere so I don't think anything will
OL,9,Fchange. It will just stay the same
OL,10,Funfortunately for here.
OL,12,F"There's so many things that need
OL,13,Fdoing we're in that bad a state. He's
OL,14,Fgot a hell of a job and I don't think
OL,15,Fhe's going to be able to do it."
OL,17,FAnother man said Andy Burnham is too
OL,18,Ffocused on Manchester, and he's
OL,19,Fsceptical on what he will do for
OL,20,Felsewhere in the North West.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FHe said: "We've not seen much of him
OL,7,Fround here. I hope he makes a
OL,8,Fdifference, I hope he's going to be a
OL,9,FPrime Minister for all of us not just
OL,10,Ffor some."
OL,12,FOne woman who works in childcare said
OL,13,Fshe hopes he will make areas safer for
OL,14,Fchildren.
OL,16,FFurther down the River Mersey, there
OL,17,Fwere more mixed views.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FOne woman in Liverpool told ITV News:
OL,7,F"He's not our Prime Minister and he's
OL,8,Fnot been elected." She also called Mr
OL,9,FBurnham's hope to keep his Everton
OL,10,Fseason ticket "a gimick".
OL,12,FAnother woman said: "I hope he can
OL,13,Fonly be good." She said "it's good"
OL,14,Fthat Mr Burnham plans to bring Number
OL,15,F10 up North, hoping "that will bring
OL,16,Fsomething to Liverpool as well."
OL,18,FAnother said she's "made up" and that
OL,19,F"anything is better than the other
OL,20,Ffella."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
