FL,370,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1784650721
OL,3,C'Time will tell': What do North West
OL,4,Cvoters think of Andy Burnham?
OL,6,FOne couple said they hope people give
OL,7,Fhim a chance, but they hope he focuses
OL,8,Fon Liverpool and beyond as well as
OL,9,FManchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
